10/11/2005
ATHENS, Greece -- Prime Minister Costas Karamanlis kicked off a four-day official visit to Japan on Wednesday (9 November).
In Tokyo, Karamanlis is to hold talks with Japanese counterpart Junichiro Koizumi and other senior representatives.
They are focusing on major international issues as well as ways to boost bilateral economic ties.
(ANA, MPA - 09/11/05)
